Package: RAgroClim
Version: 0.1-1 
Date: 2019-08-01 
Title: Agroclimatic indicators for assessment of (un)favourable weather conditions during crop growing season. 
Authors@R: c(person("Andrej", "Ceglar", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "andrej.ceglar@ec.europa.eu"), 
             person("Marian", "Bratu", role = c("cre"), email = "marian.bratu@ext.ec.europa.eu")
